<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總算等到萬聖節這一天了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你已經準備好<delay8 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要給我的糖果了嗎～？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天終於迎來萬聖節了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我為了能吃糖果吃到飽，<delay20 />
所以飯吃得比較少喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天就是期待已久的萬聖節囉！<delay frames="40" />
大家會打扮成什麼樣子呢？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay8 />好期待喔～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00">萬聖節很快就要開始囉！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已經準備好了，<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />接下來只剩換裝啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再一下下，就有糖果<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay8 />不是！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再一下下就是萬聖節啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00">萬聖節馬上就要開始了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到時候我要去嚇很多人！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay8 />我好興奮喔～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我剛剛<delay20 />有看到有萬聖節的裝飾
被人放在外面喔～<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大家似乎都<delay8 />很享受萬聖節，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也來裝飾點東西好了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">萬聖節的裝飾看起來<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還挺用心的呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過<delay8 />如果再裝飾更多更多的裝飾品，<delay20 />
萬聖節活動正式開始時，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也能更加更加地熱鬧吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光是看著這麼多的萬聖節裝飾，<delay20 />
就讓人心跳不已呢～<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />裝飾這些東西的人<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一定很期待萬聖節吧，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">島上到處都是萬聖節裝飾，<delay8 />
<anim id="Clapping" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看起來好熱鬧喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多虧這樣，我現在的萬聖節情緒
已經高漲到最高點了。<delay20 />
好期待活動正式開始的時候啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>